HEADWORD: Physicochemical
<hw>Phys`i*co*chem"ic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Physico-</ets> + <ets>chemical</ets>.]</ety> <def>Involving
the principles of both physics and chemistry; dependent on, or produced
by, the joint action of physical and chemical agencies.</def>
<rj><au>Huxley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
